Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the Millennium Puzzle complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The young boy Yugi Mutou became a master of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was challenged by a person that has a Millennium Item like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the owner of the Millennium Eye, Pegasus, and went to the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save the soul of Sugoroku, that was stolen by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Together with his friends and with his other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gods of Thunder, Water, and Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to gather your power and revive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Triple Demon God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GATE GUARDIAN!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys will have to fight our combined power first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,COME!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dragon of the Devil:\N Black Demon's Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! There's nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THUNDER SHOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. We defeated Flame Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Card Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This protects the Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate Guardian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reflection!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Storm Barricade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate Guardian is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...untouchable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the {\i1}other{\i0} Monsters on your board aren't safe from the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Tamer is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great job you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's nowhere in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got to be hiding somewhere down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just wait at guard in front of Mokuba's cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you keep searching for Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun, focus on the enemy's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 3 parts of thunder, water, and wind that make up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Triple Demon has three separate parts each holding their own Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we destroy it section by section, we can defeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Swordsman! Use Salamandra's fire and attack the Demon Wind God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool. Don't underestimate the power \Nof the Triple Demon God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch a counter-attack against Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician can avoid the attack\Nby hiding in the hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's impossible for Flame Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's a water-based attack,\Nthe Fire-type will receive a 300 point penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Swordsman is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We almost made it out of the labyrinth too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this turn wasn't a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play Demon's Summon and follow in the Flame Swordsman's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did not even get close to Gate Guardian's....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The footsteps have already been placed in the maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground of the maze was flooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means....!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Lightning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless! It's impossible for you\Nto break through Gate Guardian's Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me re-introduce you to the Water Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reflection!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't the Black Magician get attacked while inside the Magic Silk Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That second this Trap Card was activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hexagram Curse was attached to the Black Magician all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tr-Trap Card!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hexagram Curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their Attack is lowered by 700 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water section is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that! Thunder, water and wind were all no match for Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ALRIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to beat it, we need to do it from the bottom up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Remove Trap card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hexagram Curse is canceled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gate Guardian is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-kun, it's time to play our trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I play the Fusion Magic Card I had hidden on the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuse with Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-that is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Demon's Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our team's ultimate Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. What will you do, Labyrinth Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys laughing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools. What can that monster possibly do to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flying type Black Demon's Dragon\Ncan't move around in the maze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Only walking units can move\Nabout in the Maze Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, it looks like I screwed up big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I've got a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd find a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just drew a scary card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Card Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said Force?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a legendary ultra-rare\NMagic Card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card steals half of the\Nopponent's Life Points
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and adds them to the Attack Points\Nof any Monster you choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?! \N{\i1}Half{\i0} our Life Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Attack Points of Gate Guardian go up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am unable to attack in the same\Nturn I played this Magic Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But next turn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I combine the power of thunder and wind, the result will be devastating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do,\Nnext turn you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun, I told you that we still have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. This turn I'll move Black Magician\Ninto the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician, advance 7 spaces!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish. Don't forget that the second you exit this maze
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our Gate Guardian is waiting there to attack you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! We'll continue to press on no matter\Nwhat obstacles stand in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's a shred of chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that we've left the maze!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play this card on the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what monster you've revived,\NIt's too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate Guardian, attack Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combo attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MAGIC SHOCK WAVE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright. Once we defeat Black Magician,\NYugi's Life Points will drop to 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attack is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Water God, Reflection!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Water Wall we created makes your Magic Whirlwind invalid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used his Resurrection of the Dead card to revive the Demon Water God, Suuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's become their ally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great move man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made it through this round...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though they made it through this turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards... our attacks did nothing against them....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! It's Jounouchi-kun's turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There has to be...\NThere has to be a way to defeat it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next turn, they'll definitely destroy Suuga....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, there's no way for me to stop their attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything depends on\NJounouchi-kun's next card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mimic Illusionist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It copies any card played on the board...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this card to give you pay back from that Force earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take half your Life Points
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and add them to our guy's Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Black Demon's Dragon's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! How many times must I say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:13:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Demon's Dragon is not allowed to cross the maze!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use Demon Wind God Hyuga's wind to attack the Water Demon Suuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reflection!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd use that trick...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Shot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suuga can only use its Reflection once per turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you've got no way to block our attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next turn, we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you realize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know the real reason\NI brought Black Magician out of the maze?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster Replace Magic Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card switches my Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,placing the ones with the highest Attack Points in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets even one monster out of the maze...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can switch that one with any other monster he has?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the Attack Points of Suuga added
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can't stand up to the powered up Black Demon's Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YAHOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 STAR CHIPS!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We earned the right to the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game is still not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FINISHED YET!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother? Is that you, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always believed you'd save me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always be together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I didn't give anyone the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I protected Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'll get you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's touching to see you two together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you told me you were coming, I would have arranged for a better welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the cold treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have as many Star Chips as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, are you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only if you actually walk out of this labyrinth have you actually obtained victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, why don't you tell us which door leads out of the labyrinth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll tell you only one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one of these is the real door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair. You two {\i1}lost{\i0}! You should tell us which is the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Which is the real door!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd be like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Yugi. What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use these to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he depends on God in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold a coin in both my right and left hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coin that remains in my hand\Nwill decide what door we pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus... I don't know what you're planning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't let you have Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me this {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(158,445)}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the 'Ze' coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the one in your hand is 'Ma'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've chosen 'Ma'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... Which one's the right one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Ma'.... Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Ze'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The right answer is....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the 'ze' door!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There {\i1}is{\i0} no right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I picked 'Ma', you'd say 'ze'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I chose 'ze', you'd say 'Ma'!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, you could not say the right answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We win the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I chose...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is 'Ze!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coin in my hand wasn't just marked 'Ma'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only 'Ze' is a single-sided coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the start, this coin was marked as\Nboth 'Ma' and 'ze'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't honest about which hand\Nheld the double-sided coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YES! Everyone onto Pegasus's castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a small trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! What did you do to Mokuba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Soul Sealing Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be looking after Mokuba boy's soul for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want Mokuba boy back,\Nyou'll have to defeat me in a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I challenge you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you must fight with Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only face me\Nif you defeat Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(131,143)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We defeated the Maze Brothers' trap and finally\Ngot out of the maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Yugi's in a Duel, he's always so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But normally, he's not very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must hurry to Pegasus's castle.\NThere's not much time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that Kaiba-kun blocking the castle's gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to duel on top of the castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! "The Destined Duel! Yugi VS Kaiba"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:22:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship

